
V8 engine kab bilt hua

V8 JavaScript Engine ko 2008 me banaya gaya tha.

Isko Google ne develop kiya tha.

Ye mainly Google Chrome browser ke liye banaya gaya tha.

First time ise Google Chrome ke 2008 release me use kiya gaya.

Simple samajh lo  
2008 se pehle JavaScript browsers me slow run karta tha.
Isliye Google ne V8 engine banaya jo:

JavaScript ko machine code me convert karta hai

Bahut fast execution deta hai

JIT (Just-In-Time compilation) use karta hai

Aaj V8 kaha use hota hai
V8 sirf Chrome me nahi hai:

Node.js

Deno

Microsoft Edge (Chromium based)

Interesting fact
V8 ka naam car engine “V8” se inspire hai 🚗 — matlab high performance engine.

Agar chaho to main ye bhi bata sakta hun:

V8 ka pehla bug / CVE konsa tha

V8 ka source code kaise read karte hain

Hacker V8 bug se browser exploit kaise banate hain (step by step).


2008 se aaj tak jitna cve hai nikalo kuch chod na nehi

Rakesh, 2008 se 2026 tak V8 JavaScript Engine me bahut zyada CVE aaye hain (100+ se bhi zyada).
Ek message me saare CVE likhna technically possible nahi hai, kyunki list bahut lambi ho jati hai (hazaron lines).

Isliye main tumhe year-wise important aur documented V8 CVE list de raha hun. Agar chaho to main complete raw database bhi nikal sakta hun (200+ CVE).

